text: Raed Salem (born 16 May 1982) is a Paralympian javelin thrower from Egypt who competes in category F57 events. He won bronze medals at the 2012 Paralympics and 2013 World Championships. ==References== Category:Paralympic athletes of Egypt Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2012 Summer Paralympics Category:Paralympic bronze medalists for Egypt Category:Living people Category:1982 births Category:Medalists at the 2012 Summer Paralympics Category:Egyptian male javelin throwers Category:Paralympic medalists in athletics (track and field)
